Texts.Chs: 请制作一些基本的物品，如^orange;线圈^reset;、^orange;电路板^reset;，又或者非常有用的^orange;物质萃取器^reset;。还有如果你可以升级^orange;加工台^reset;，请不要犹豫。
Texts.Eng: Try building a few more basic goods such as a ^orange;coil, circuitboard^reset; or an extremely useful ^orange;Extraction Lab^reset;. ^orange;The Machining Table and its upgrades^reset; are necessary for ^orange;every FU crafting station^reset;. Use it well.

Texts.Chs: 恭喜你在^cyan;Frackin'Universe^reset;成功踏出了第一步。用^orange;加工台^reset;你可以制作^orange;各种实验设备以及部分基础材料^reset;。首先让我们制作^orange;9个铜线^reset;吧。
Texts.Eng: You've taken your first steps in ^cyan;Frackin' Universe^reset;. With the ^orange;Machining Table^reset; you can now branch out into a wide assortment of ^orange;Lab Stations and Equipment^reset; as well as ^green;crafting resources^reset;. Let's start by making ^orange;9 copper wire^reset;.
